---
import { refreshAuthFromCookie } from '../../lib/auth';
import { getPublicStorePath, getStoreAdminPath } from '../../lib/adminRoutes';
import { requireCurrentStoreForAdmin } from '../../lib/storeContext';
import AdminSidebar from '../../components/admin/AdminSidebar.astro';

// PZ-ADMIN-PRODUCTS-V26-10-OFERTA-TARJETA-GRIS-20260605
// PZ-PRODUCTOS-ADMIN-V45-FIX-OFERTA-REGULAR-BLOQUEADO-20260605
const pocketbaseUrl = import.meta.env.PUBLIC_POCKETBASE_URL;
const authPb = await refreshAuthFromCookie(Astro.request.headers.get('cookie') || '');
const adminContext = await requireCurrentStoreForAdmin(authPb);
const currentStoreId = adminContext.storeId;
const adminAuthToken = authPb.authStore.token;
const currentStoreSlug = adminContext.store.slug || '';
const currentStoreName = adminContext.store.name || adminContext.store.title || currentStoreSlug || 'Tienda';
const adminBasePath = getStoreAdminPath(currentStoreSlug);
const adminCatalogPath = getStoreAdminPath(currentStoreSlug, 'catalog');
const adminProductsPath = getStoreAdminPath(currentStoreSlug, 'products');
const adminOrdersPath = getStoreAdminPath(currentStoreSlug, 'orders');
const adminStoreSettingsPath = getStoreAdminPath(currentStoreSlug, 'store-settings');
const adminGiftsPath = getStoreAdminPath(currentStoreSlug, 'gifts');
const adminShippingPath = getStoreAdminPath(currentStoreSlug, 'shipping');
const adminPromosPath = getStoreAdminPath(currentStoreSlug, 'promos');
const adminOrganizationPath = getStoreAdminPath(currentStoreSlug, 'organization');
const publicStorePath = getPublicStorePath(currentStoreSlug);
const masterSupportWhatsapp = String(import.meta.env.PUBLIC_MASTER_SUPPORT_WHATSAPP || '').replace(/[^0-9]/g, '');
const masterSupportEmail = String(import.meta.env.PUBLIC_MASTER_SUPPORT_EMAIL || '').trim();
const supportMessage = `Hola soporte de Tu Senda 84, necesito ayuda con el admin de productos de la tienda ${currentStoreName} (${currentStoreSlug || 'sin-slug'}).`;
const masterSupportHref = masterSupportWhatsapp
  ? `https://wa.me/${masterSupportWhatsapp}?text=${encodeURIComponent(supportMessage)}`
  : (masterSupportEmail ? `mailto:${masterSupportEmail}?subject=${encodeURIComponent('Soporte Productos Tu Senda 84')}&body=${encodeURIComponent(supportMessage)}` : '');
const masterSupportLabel = masterSupportHref ? 'Contactar a soporte' : 'Soporte Tu Senda 84';
---
<!-- PZ-PRODUCTOS-INFO-ADICIONAL-V6-20260603
  Cambio: guarda Información adicional con PATCH JSON y requiere migración final extra_info.
-->
<!-- PZ-AJUSTES-GENERALES-PUBLICOS-MENU-PUBLICO-V5-20260603
  Cambio: se eliminó de forma general la opción/texto "Tienda pública" del sidebar admin.
-->
<!-- PZ-PRODUCTOS-V25-VISTA-VARIACIONES-20260601
  Bloque: Gestión de catálogo - Crear y editar productos
  Cambio base: formulario real para crear y editar productos en la plataforma desde /admin/products.
  V3: Limpieza visual: al crear o editar se ocultan resumen, buscador y listado de productos existentes.
  V4: Categoría y subcategoría se pueden crear rápido desde el formulario de producto, con foto opcional.
  V5: Creación rápida movida a modal flotante sin salir del producto.
  V6: Modal flotante con estilo de tarjeta premium.
  V7: Corrección de cierre del modal: botón X funcional, clic fuera de la tarjeta cierra el modal y Escape mantiene cierre seguro.
  V8: Placeholder del nombre cambiado a "Ej: Nombre del producto".
  V9: En el listado, tocar miniatura o nombre del producto abre edición.
  V10: Agrega botón Borrar en el listado con confirmación segura antes de eliminar el producto.
  V11: Corrige Ocultar/Activar para no abrir edición y cierra el formulario al guardar correctamente.
  V12: Stock 0 se muestra como Agotado sin ocultar el producto.
  V13: Limpia acciones del listado con menú flotante, agrega Marcar agotado y permite preorder cuando stock está en 0.
  V14: Corrige menú de 3 puntos para que no quede escondido al final del listado; se posiciona como flotante y abre hacia arriba si hace falta.
  V15: Agrega gestión admin de variaciones por producto: crear, editar, ocultar/activar, borrar, foto, precio, costo, stock, ref interna, preorder y orden visual.
  V16: Mantiene el menú de variaciones funcional y permite borrar productos con variaciones borrando primero sus variaciones reales. Las órdenes conservan historial fijo en order_items.
  V17: Agrega control de stock descontable, valida Guardar según nombre/stock/variaciones, permite producto sin categoría visible en inicio y sincroniza stock padre con la suma de variaciones.
  V19: Corrige validaciones de variaciones, categoría opcional visible, stock padre automático y limpia el panel de variaciones con edición bajo demanda y flechas de orden.
  V20: Oculta “Usa variaciones” durante creación; después de guardar pregunta si desea agregar variaciones antes de cerrar el panel.
  V21: Cambia confirmaciones por paneles flotantes dentro de la tarjeta: agregar variaciones post-guardado y borrar producto. Refuerza stock=0 seguro cuando no descuenta stock.
  V36: Oculta “Usa variaciones” desde el HTML inicial al crear producto nuevo; solo se muestra al editar productos existentes.
  V33: Corrige creación de producto nuevo con stock descontable: botón Guardar directo sin bloqueo HTML y creación segura en dos pasos.
  V34: Evita productos repetidos, busca por ref interna y unifica Marcar agotado con estilo/confirmación tipo Borrar.
  V35: Agrega alerta flotante premium “Producto repetido” al intentar crear/guardar duplicados.
  V37: Agrega oferta con precio de oferta USD, visible en tienda pública, carrito y checkout.
-->
<!doctype html>
<html lang="es">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>Productos | PowerZona</title>
    <link rel="icon" type="image/svg+xml" href="/favicon.svg" />
    <style is:global>
      :root {
        font-family: Inter, ui-sans-serif, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Segoe UI", sans-serif;
        --page: #eef3f9;
        --surface: #ffffff;
        --surface-soft: #f8fafc;
        --text: #0f172a;
        --muted: #64748b;
        --border: #e2e8f0;
        --green: #16a34a;
        --blue: #2563eb;
        --red: #dc2626;
        --orange: #f97316;
        --purple: #7c3aed;
        --shadow: 0 18px 45px rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.08);
      }

      * { box-sizing: border-box; }
      html, body { margin: 0; min-height: 100%; }
      body {
        color: var(--text);
        background:
          radial-gradient(circle at 14% 0%, rgba(37, 99, 235, 0.16), transparent 30%),
          radial-gradient(circle at 85% 8%, rgba(22, 163, 74, 0.10), transparent 25%),
          linear-gradient(180deg, #f8fbff 0%, var(--page) 48%, #e8eef7 100%);
      }

      a { color: inherit; text-decoration: none; }
      button, input, select { font: inherit; }
      button { cursor: pointer; }
      button:disabled { cursor: not-allowed; opacity: .65; }
      .hidden { display: none !important; }

      .app-shell { width: min(1480px, 100%); margin: 0 auto; padding: 24px; display: block; }
      .sidebar-overlay {
        position: fixed; inset: 0; z-index: 80; background: rgba(15, 23, 42, .36);
        opacity: 0; pointer-events: none; transition: opacity .22s ease; backdrop-filter: blur(2px);
      }
      body.sidebar-open .sidebar-overlay { opacity: 1; pointer-events: auto; }
      .sidebar {
        position: fixed; top: 18px; left: 18px; bottom: 18px; z-index: 90; width: min(286px, calc(100vw - 36px));
        border-radius: 30px; padding: 18px; background: linear-gradient(180deg, #ffffff 0%, #f8fafc 100%);
        color: #0f172a; border: 1px solid rgba(226, 232, 240, .95); box-shadow: 0 28px 80px rgba(15, 23, 42, .22);
        overflow: hidden; transform: translateX(calc(-100% - 28px)); transition: transform .24s ease;
      }
      body.sidebar-open .sidebar { transform: translateX(0); }
      .sidebar::before { content: ''; position: absolute; inset: 0; background: radial-gradient(circle at 18% 0%, rgba(15,23,42,.06), transparent 32%); pointer-events: none; }
      .sidebar-inner { position: relative; z-index: 1; display: flex; flex-direction: column; height: 100%; min-height: 0; }
      .brand { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 11px; padding: 8px 8px 18px; border-bottom: 1px solid #e2e8f0; margin-bottom: 14px; }
      .brand-logo { width: 42px; height: 42px; border-radius: 16px; display: inline-flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; background: #0f172a; color: #fff; box-shadow: 0 14px 30px rgba(15, 23, 42, .18); font-weight: 1000; }
      .brand-title { margin: 0; font-size: 15px; font-weight: 1000; letter-spacing: -.02em; }
      .brand-subtitle { margin: 2px 0 0; color: #64748b; font-size: 11px; font-weight: 850; }
      .sidebar-label { margin: 18px 9px 9px; color: #64748b; font-size: 10px; font-weight: 1000; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: .12em; }
      .nav-list { display: grid; gap: 8px; }
      .nav-item { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 11px; padding: 11px 12px; border-radius: 18px; color: #334155; font-size: 13px; font-weight: 950; border: 1px solid transparent; }
      .nav-item:hover { background: #f1f5f9; border-color: #e2e8f0; color: #0f172a; }
      .nav-item.active { background: #0f172a; border-color: #0f172a; color: #fff; box-shadow: 0 12px 26px rgba(15,23,42,.16); }
      .nav-icon { width: 34px; height: 34px; border-radius: 14px; display: inline-flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; background: #f8fafc; color: #0f172a; border: 1px solid #e2e8f0; flex: 0 0 auto; }
      .nav-icon svg { width: 18px; height: 18px; display: block; fill: currentColor; }
      .nav-item.active .nav-icon { background: rgba(255,255,255,.12); color: #fff; border-color: rgba(255,255,255,.20); }
      .sidebar-footer { margin-top: auto; padding: 14px; border-radius: 22px; background: #f8fafc; border: 1px solid #e2e8f0; }
      .sidebar-footer strong { display: block; font-size: 12px; margin-bottom: 5px; color: #0f172a; }
      .sidebar-footer span { display: block; color: #475569; font-size: 11px; line-height: 1.45; font-weight: 750; }
      .sidebar-close { margin-left: auto; width: 36px; height: 36px; border-radius: 14px; border: 1px solid #e2e8f0; background: #fff; color: #0f172a; font-weight: 1000; box-shadow: 0 8px 18px rgba(15,23,42,.05); }
      .menu-btn { display: inline-flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; gap: 10px; border-radius: 18px; padding: 12px 15px; background: #0f172a; color: #fff; border: 1px solid #0f172a; box-shadow: 0 12px 26px rgba(15,23,42,.16); font-weight: 1000; }

      .main-wrap { min-width: 0; padding: 2px 0 28px; }
      .topbar { display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: space-between; gap: 14px; margin-bottom: 18px; flex-wrap: wrap; }
      .action-btn, .mini-btn {
        display: inline-flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; gap: 9px;
        border-radius: 16px; padding: 11px 14px; background: rgba(255,255,255,.92);
        border: 1px solid rgba(226, 232, 240, 0.95); box-shadow: 0 12px 26px rgba(15,23,42,.07); font-weight: 950;
      }
      .action-btn.dark, .mini-btn.primary { background: #0f172a; color: #fff; border-color: #0f172a; }
      .action-btn.danger, .mini-btn.danger { background: #fee2e2; color: #991b1b; border-color: #fecaca; }
      .mini-btn.danger:hover { background: #fecaca; }
      .hero-actions { display: flex; gap: 10px; flex-wrap: wrap; justify-content: flex-end; position: relative; z-index: 1; }
      .hero-card, .panel-card, .list-card { background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.92); border: 1px solid rgba(226, 232, 240, 0.96); border-radius: 30px; box-shadow: var(--shadow); backdrop-filter: blur(10px); }
      .hero-card { padding: 26px; margin-bottom: 18px; display: grid; grid-template-columns: minmax(0, 1fr) auto; gap: 18px; align-items: center; position: relative; overflow: hidden; }
      .hero-card::after { content: ''; position: absolute; right: -80px; top: -90px; width: 230px; height: 230px; background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(37,99,235,.16), transparent 66%); pointer-events: none; }
      .badge { display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 8px; border-radius: 999px; padding: 8px 12px; background: #dcfce7; color: #166534; font-size: 13px; font-weight: 1000; }
      .page-title { font-size: clamp(25px, 3vw, 40px); font-weight: 1000; letter-spacing: -0.045em; line-height: 1.05; margin: 14px 0 0; }
      .page-title span { color: #334155; font-weight: 800; }
      .page-subtitle { margin: 9px 0 0; font-size: 15px; color: var(--muted); line-height: 1.55; max-width: 820px; }
      .panel-card { padding: 22px; }
      .login-card { max-width: 520px; margin: 28px auto; }
      .form-grid { display: grid; gap: 12px; }
      .field { display: grid; gap: 7px; }
      .field label { color: #334155; font-size: 12px; font-weight: 950; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: .04em; }
      .field input, .field select { width: 100%; border: 1px solid var(--border); border-radius: 16px; background: #fff; color: var(--text); padding: 12px 13px; outline: none; font-weight: 800; box-shadow: inset 0 1px 0 rgba(15,23,42,.02); }
      .submit-btn { border: 0; border-radius: 16px; padding: 12px 16px; background: linear-gradient(135deg, #0f172a, #1e293b); color: #fff; font-weight: 1000; box-shadow: 0 14px 28px rgba(15,23,42,.20); }
      .alert { margin-top: 12px; border-radius: 16px; padding: 11px 12px; font-size: 13px; font-weight: 850; line-height: 1.45; }
      .alert-info { background: #eff6ff; color: #1e40af; border: 1px solid #bfdbfe; }
      .alert-success { background: #dcfce7; color: #166534; border: 1px solid #bbf7d0; }
      .alert-error { background: #fee2e2; color: #991b1b; border: 1px solid #fecaca; }

      .duplicate-toast {
        position: fixed;
        right: 22px;
        bottom: 22px;
        z-index: 9999;
        display: inline-flex;
        align-items: center;
        gap: 10px;
        max-width: min(420px, calc(100vw - 32px));
        border: 1px solid #fecaca;
        border-radius: 999px;
        background: linear-gradient(135deg, #fee2e2, #fff7f7);
        color: #991b1b;
        padding: 12px 15px;
        box-shadow: 0 20px 44px rgba(153, 27, 27, .18);
        font-size: 13px;
        font-weight: 1000;
        letter-spacing: -.01em;
        transform: translateY(0);
        opacity: 1;
        transition: opacity .18s ease, transform .18s ease;
      }
      .duplicate-toast.hidden { display: none; }
      .duplicate-toast-icon {
        width: 28px;
        height: 28px;
        border-radius: 999px;
        display: inline-flex;
        align-items: center;
        justify-content: center;
        background: #991b1b;
        color: #fff;
        flex: 0 0 auto;
        box-shadow: 0 10px 22px rgba(153, 27, 27, .20);
      }
      .duplicate-toast strong { display: block; line-height: 1.05; }
      .duplicate-toast span:last-child { display: block; margin-top: 2px; font-size: 11px; font-weight: 850; color: #7f1d1d; }

      .stats-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(4, minmax(0, 1fr)); gap: 14px; margin-bottom: 18px; }
      .stat-card { position: relative; overflow: hidden; padding: 18px; border-radius: 24px; background: rgba(255,255,255,.94); border: 1px solid rgba(226,232,240,.96); box-shadow: 0 14px 34px rgba(15,23,42,.06); }
      .stat-card::after { content: ""; position: absolute; right: 16px; top: 16px; width: 38px; height: 38px; border-radius: 14px; background: #eff6ff; border: 1px solid #dbeafe; }
      .stat-card.ok::after { background: #dcfce7; border-color: #bbf7d0; }
      .stat-card.warn::after { background: #ffedd5; border-color: #fed7aa; }
      .stat-card.muted::after { background: #f1f5f9; border-color: #e2e8f0; }
      .stat-label { margin: 0; color: var(--muted); font-size: 12px; font-weight: 950; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: .05em; }
      .stat-value { margin: 7px 0 0; font-size: 25px; font-weight: 1000; letter-spacing: -.04em; }
      .toolbar { padding: 18px; display: grid; grid-template-columns: minmax(220px, 1.2fr) minmax(150px, .7fr) minmax(150px, .7fr) minmax(140px, .55fr) minmax(130px, .5fr) auto; gap: 12px; align-items: end; margin-bottom: 18px; }
      .list-head { display: grid; grid-template-columns: minmax(260px, 1.2fr) minmax(180px, .65fr) minmax(130px, .45fr) minmax(135px, .4fr) minmax(120px, .4fr) minmax(180px, auto); gap: 14px; padding: 14px 18px; border-bottom: 1px solid #eef2f7; color: #64748b; font-size: 11px; font-weight: 1000; letter-spacing: .08em; text-transform: uppercase; }
      .products-list { display: grid; gap: 0; overflow: visible; }
      .product-row { display: grid; grid-template-columns: minmax(260px, 1.2fr) minmax(180px, .65fr) minmax(130px, .45fr) minmax(135px, .4fr) minmax(120px, .4fr) minmax(180px, auto); gap: 14px; align-items: center; padding: 16px 18px; border-bottom: 1px solid #eef2f7; }
      .product-row:last-child { border-bottom: 0; }
      .product-row:hover { background: #fbfdff; }
      .product-main { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 12px; min-width: 0; }
      .product-thumb { width: 58px; height: 58px; border-radius: 16px; object-fit: contain; flex: 0 0 58px; border: 1px solid #e2e8f0; background: #f1f5f9; box-shadow: 0 8px 18px rgba(15,23,42,.08); }
      .product-thumb.placeholder { display: inline-flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; color: #94a3b8; font-size: 22px; font-weight: 1000; }
      .product-title { margin: 0; font-size: 15px; font-weight: 1000; letter-spacing: -.02em; }
      .product-title.js-product-open, .product-thumb.js-product-open { cursor: pointer; }
      .product-title.js-product-open:hover { text-decoration: underline; text-underline-offset: 3px; }
      .product-meta { margin: 5px 0 0; color: var(--muted); font-size: 12px; font-weight: 750; word-break: break-word; }
      .pill { display: inline-flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; border-radius: 999px; padding: 8px 10px; font-size: 11px; font-weight: 1000; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: .035em; border: 1px solid transparent; white-space: nowrap; }
      .pill-visible { background: #dcfce7; color: #166534; border-color: #bbf7d0; }
      .pill-hidden { background: #fee2e2; color: #991b1b; border-color: #fecaca; }
      .pill-soldout { background: #ffedd5; color: #9a3412; border-color: #fed7aa; }
      .price { font-size: 15px; font-weight: 1000; }
      .stock { font-size: 15px; font-weight: 950; color: #334155; }
      .category-cell { min-width: 0; }
      .category-name { display: block; color: #0f172a; font-size: 13px; font-weight: 1000; white-space: nowrap; overflow: hidden; text-overflow: ellipsis; }
      .category-sub { display: block; margin-top: 4px; color: #64748b; font-size: 12px; font-weight: 800; white-space: nowrap; overflow: hidden; text-overflow: ellipsis; }
      .row-actions { display: flex; justify-content: flex-end; gap: 8px; flex-wrap: wrap; position: relative; }
      .actions-wrap { position: relative; display: inline-flex; justify-content: flex-end; }
      .actions-trigger { min-width: 44px; padding-inline: 13px; font-size: 18px; line-height: 1; }
      .actions-menu {
        position: absolute;
        top: calc(100% + 8px);
        right: 0;
        z-index: 3000;
        width: 210px;
        padding: 8px;
        border-radius: 20px;
        border: 1px solid rgba(226,232,240,.96);
        background: rgba(255,255,255,.98);
        box-shadow: 0 22px 55px rgba(15,23,42,.18);
      }
      .actions-menu.open-up {
        top: auto;
        bottom: calc(100% + 8px);
      }
      .actions-menu::before { display: none; }
      .actions-menu button {
        width: 100%;
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        justify-content: space-between;
        gap: 10px;
        border: 0;
        border-radius: 14px;
        background: transparent;
        padding: 10px 11px;
        color: #334155;
        font-size: 13px;
        font-weight: 950;
        text-align: left;
      }
      .actions-menu button:hover { background: #f1f5f9; color: #0f172a; }
      .actions-menu button.danger-action { color: #991b1b; }
      .actions-menu button.danger-action:hover { background: #fee2e2; }
      .actions-menu button:disabled { color: #94a3b8; background: transparent; opacity: .75; }

      .editor-card { padding: 0; overflow: hidden; margin-bottom: 18px; }
      .editor-head { display: flex; align-items: flex-start; justify-content: space-between; gap: 14px; padding: 20px 22px; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border); background: linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(248,250,252,.92), rgba(255,255,255,.72)); }
      .editor-title { margin: 0; font-size: 20px; font-weight: 1000; letter-spacing: -.03em; }
      .editor-subtitle { margin: 6px 0 0; color: var(--muted); font-size: 13px; line-height: 1.45; font-weight: 800; }
      .editor-body { padding: 20px 22px 22px; }
      .product-form-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(2, minmax(0, 1fr)); gap: 14px; }
      .product-form-grid .full { grid-column: 1 / -1; }
      .field textarea { width: 100%; min-height: 118px; resize: vertical; border: 1px solid var(--border); border-radius: 16px; background: #fff; color: var(--text); padding: 12px 13px; outline: none; font-weight: 750; line-height: 1.5; box-shadow: inset 0 1px 0 rgba(15,23,42,.02); }
      .field textarea:focus { border-color: #93c5fd; box-shadow: 0 0 0 4px rgba(37, 99, 235, .12); }
      .field input[type="file"] { padding: 10px; background: #f8fafc; }
      .check-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(4, minmax(0, 1fr)); gap: 10px; }
      .check-card { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 10px; border: 1px solid var(--border); border-radius: 18px; background: #fff; padding: 12px 13px; color: #334155; font-weight: 900; }
      .check-card input { width: 18px; height: 18px; accent-color: #16a34a; }
      .price-offer-card { grid-column: 1 / -1; border: 1px solid rgba(15, 23, 42, .10); background: linear-gradient(180deg, #fff 0%, #f8fafc 100%); border-radius: 22px; padding: 14px; box-shadow: 0 16px 38px rgba(15,23,42,.06); }
      .price-offer-card-head { display:flex; justify-content:space-between; align-items:flex-start; gap:12px; margin-bottom:12px; }
      .price-offer-card-title { margin:0; font-size:14px; font-weight:1000; color:#0f172a; letter-spacing:-.01em; }
      .price-offer-card-subtitle { margin:4px 0 0; color:#64748b; font-size:12px; line-height:1.35; font-weight:750; }
      .price-offer-grid { display:grid; grid-template-columns: minmax(0, 1fr) minmax(0, 1fr); gap:12px; align-items:start; }
      .offer-field { border: 1px solid rgba(220, 38, 38, .16); background: linear-gradient(180deg, #fff 0%, #fff7f7 100%); border-radius: 20px; padding: 12px; }
      .offer-field .offer-hint { margin: 7px 0 0; color: #16a34a; font-size: 12px; font-weight: 900; }
